---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Volvo Premium Prime Mover 2026: Luxury Comfort and Performance',
  slug: 'volvo-premium-2026',
  excerpt: 'Finance Volvo FH premium prime movers with 0% down payment. Superior comfort, fuel economy, and resale value for long-distance haulage.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['volvo prime mover', 'premium truck financing', 'luxury prime mover', '0% down payment', 'long distance haulage'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Volvo FH: Premium Prime Mover Excellence</h2>

      <p>Volvo FH represents the pinnacle of prime mover luxury. Swedish engineering meets driver comfort. Superior fuel economy. Exceptional safety features. Highest resale value among all brands. Premium pricing delivers premium returns for serious transport operators.</p>

      <h2>Volvo FH Specifications</h2>

      <h3>Key Features</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine:</strong> D13 13L diesel, 420 HP, 2,100 Nm torque</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> I-Shift 12-speed automated</li>
        <li><strong>Fuel Consumption:</strong> 32L/100km (best in class)</li>
        <li><strong>New Price:</strong> RM450,000-RM500,000</li>
        <li><strong>Used (7-10 years):</strong> RM200,000-RM250,000</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Premium Features</h2>

      <h3>Driver Comfort</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Premium leather seats with massage</li>
        <li>Fully adjustable steering wheel</li>
        <li>Climate control</li>
        <li>Fridge compartment</li>
        <li>Cruise control</li>
        <li>Quiet cabin (65dB at 100km/h)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Safety Technology</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Emergency braking</li>
        <td>Lane departure warning</li>
        <li>Adaptive cruise control</li>
        <li>Blind spot detection</li>
        <li>Stability control</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Fuel Economy Advantage</h2>

      <p><strong>Volvo FH:</strong> 32L/100km</p>

      <p><strong>Isuzu/Hino:</strong> 35-37L/100km</p>

      <p><strong>Monthly Fuel Savings (Klang-Penang, 20 trips):</strong>
  <br>• Distance: 16,000 km/month
  <br>• Volvo: 16,000 ÷ 100 × 32L = 5,120L = RM13,056
  <br>• Competitor: 16,000 ÷ 100 × 36L = 5,760L = RM14,688
  <br><strong>Savings: RM1,632 per month = RM19,584 per year</strong></p>

      <h2>Resale Value: Best in Class</h2>

      <p><strong>Volvo Depreciation:</strong> 6-8% per year (lowest)</p>

      <p><strong>Examples:</strong>
  <br>• New (RM475,000) → 5 years (RM310,000-RM340,000)
  <br>• 5 years (RM325,000) → 10 years (RM200,000-RM230,000)</p>

      <p><strong>Compare to Japanese brands:</strong> Volvo retains 10-15% more value</p>

      <h2>5-Year Cost Analysis</h2>

      <h3>Volvo FH (New, RM475,000)</h3>

      <p>• Purchase: RM475,000
  <br>• Monthly fuel: RM13,056
  <br>• Monthly maintenance: RM3,000
  <br>• Monthly financing: ~RM8,800
  <br>• Monthly total: RM24,856</p>

      <p><strong>5-Year Operating Cost:</strong> RM1,491,360</p>

      <p><strong>Resale after 5 years:</strong> RM325,000</p>

      <p><strong>Net Cost:</strong> RM1,641,360</p>

      <h3>Isuzu Giga (New, RM380,000) - Comparison</h3>

      <p>• Purchase: RM380,000
  <br>• Monthly fuel: RM14,280
  <br>• Monthly maintenance: RM2,500
  <br>• Monthly financing: ~RM7,000
  <br>• Monthly total: RM23,780</p>

      <p><strong>5-Year Operating Cost:</strong> RM1,426,800</p>

      <p><strong>Resale after 5 years:</strong> RM240,000</p>

      <p><strong>Net Cost:</strong> RM1,566,800</p>

      <h3>Result:</h3>

      <p><strong>Isuzu cheaper by:</strong> RM74,560 over 5 years</p>

      <p><strong>But Volvo offers:</strong>
  <br>• Premium comfort for driver retention
  <br>• Better fuel economy
  <br>• Higher resale value
  <br>• Superior safety</p>

      <h2>When Volvo Makes Sense</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Long-distance international haulage (Thailand, Singapore)</li>
        <li>Driver retention critical (premium comfort reduces turnover)</li>
        <li>High annual mileage (30,000+ km/month)</li>
        <li>Safety image important for corporate clients</li>
        <li>Plan to keep truck 7+ years (resale value advantage compounds)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Financing Volvo with 0% Down</h2>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng Credit:</strong>
  <br>• 0% down payment on new Volvo FH
  <br>• 100% financing
  <br>• Finance used Volvo (any age)
  <br>• 24-48 hour approval</p>

      <p><strong>Example:</strong>
  <br>• Volvo new: RM475,000, 0% down, ~RM8,800/month
  <br>• Volvo used: RM220,000, 0% down, ~RM4,000/month</p>

      <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>

      <p>Volvo FH costs RM74,560 more over 5 years than Japanese brands. But delivers superior comfort, fuel economy, and resale value. For long-distance haulage with driver retention critical, Volvo premium pays dividends.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Finance Volvo with 0% Down</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Premium prime mover financing. Approved in 24-48 hours.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Volvo Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  td {
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    padding: 0.75rem;
  }

  br {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
